data.description: Charming 4 or 5 Bedrooms, 2 Full Baths HISTORIC FARMETTE located on just under 3 ACRES is a ONE-OF-A-KIND! Home sits approx 1/4 mile off the road and offers plenty PEACE, QUIET & PRIVACY. Once inside you'll be able to see many updates thru-out this COUNTRY-STYLE home. Beautiful Refinished Original Hardwood Flooring on 1st Floor ~ Wood Burning Outside Furnace 2015 ~ Tear Off Roof 2016 ~ New Upstairs Windows 2015 ~ New Downstairs Windows 2021 ~ Both Bathrooms Updated ~ Modern conveniences but also the charm of a different time period. Large landing area upstairs(game area or ?) Basement work completed ~ Installed I Beams on partial East and West walls ~ Back Plastered repaired walls with epoxy mortar ~ Lifetime Transferable Warranty ~ 4-car garage, 15X20 shed and you can't have a farmette without a MILK HOUSE!
